      <li id="ref-radford2019">Radford et al. (2019). <a href="https://cdn.openai.com/better-language-models/language_models_are_unsupervised_multitask_learners.pdf">Language Models are Unsupervised Multitask Learners</a>. GPT-2 論文</li>
      <li><a href="https://github.com/openai/gpt-2">openai/gpt-2</a>. 公式実装 (2019)</li>
