    <h3 class="gpt2-subh">トークナイゼーションと位置エンコーディング</h3>
    <ul>
      <li id="ref-sennrich2016">Sennrich et al. (2016). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1508.07909">Neural Machine Translation of Rare Words with Subword Units</a>. BPE</li>
      <li id="ref-tao2024">Tao et al. (2024). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2407.13623">Scaling Laws with Vocabulary: Larger Models Deserve Larger Vocabularies</a>. 最適 vocab サイズの scaling law (LLaMA2-70B は 216K vocab が最適と予測)</li>
      <li id="ref-huang2025">Huang et al. (2025, ICML). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2501.16975">Over-Tokenized Transformer: Vocabulary is Generally Worth Scaling</a>. 入力/出力 vocab の分離と log-linear scaling (input vocab 128× で 400M→1B 相当)</li>
      <li id="ref-pagnoni2024">Pagnoni et al. (2024). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2412.09871">Byte Latent Transformer: Patches Scale Better Than Tokens</a>. Meta の tokenizer-free byte-level モデル (BLT)</li>
      <li id="ref-raffel2020">Raffel et al. (2020). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1910.10683">Exploring the Limits of Transfer Learning with a Unified Text-to-Text Transformer</a>. T5, 相対位置</li>
      <li id="ref-su2021">Su et al. (2021). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2104.09864">RoFormer: Enhanced Transformer with Rotary Position Embedding</a>. RoPE</li>
      <li id="ref-press2022">Press et al. (2022). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2108.12409">Train Short, Test Long: Attention with Linear Biases Enables Input Length Extrapolation</a>. ALiBi</li>
