    <ul>
      <li id="ref-sutskever2014">Sutskever et al. (2014). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1409.3215">Sequence to Sequence Learning with Neural Networks</a>. RNN encoder-decoder (seq2seq) 原論文</li>
      <li id="ref-bahdanau2014">Bahdanau et al. (2014). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1409.0473">Neural Machine Translation by Jointly Learning to Align and Translate</a>. 最初の Attention (alignment model)</li>
      <li id="ref-luong2015">Luong et al. (2015). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1508.04025">Effective Approaches to Attention-based Neural Machine Translation</a>. global/local attention の整理</li>
      <li id="ref-cheng2016">Cheng et al. (2016). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1601.06733">Long Short-Term Memory-Networks for Machine Reading</a>. Self-Attention の初期例</li>
      <li id="ref-lin2017">Lin et al. (2017). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1703.03130">A Structured Self-Attentive Sentence Embedding</a>. Self-Attention を用いた文表現</li>
      <li id="ref-he2016">He et al. (2016). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385">Deep Residual Learning for Image Recognition</a>. ResNet, 残差接続</li>
      <li id="ref-elhage2021">Elhage et al. (2021). <a href="https://transformer-circuits.pub/2021/framework/index.html">A Mathematical Framework for Transformer Circuits</a>. 残差ストリームの定式化</li>
      <li id="ref-dettmers2022">Dettmers et al. (2022). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2208.07339">LLM.int8(): 8-bit Matrix Multiplication for Transformers at Scale</a>. 外れ値 (outlier features) の解析</li>
