      <li id="ref-tying">Press &amp; Wolf (2017). <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/1608.05859">Using the Output Embedding to Improve Language Models</a>. weight tying</li>
      <li id="ref-hf-conv1d"><a href="https://github.com/huggingface/transformers/blob/main/src/transformers/pytorch_utils.py">huggingface/transformers — Conv1D</a>. HF GPT-2 が使う重みレイアウト (<code>(in, out)</code>)</li>
      <li id="ref-openai-gpt2-src"><a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/openai/gpt-2/master/src/model.py">openai/gpt-2 src/model.py</a>. 原典実装 (Conv1D の bias / LayerNorm bias / n_ctx=1024)</li>
